Package: rinspect
Title: Large Language Model Evaluation for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Simon", "Couch", , "simon.couch@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5676-5107")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: A port of 'Inspect', a widely adopted 'Python' framework for 
    large language model evaluation. Specifically aimed at 'ellmer' users who 
    want to measure the effectiveness of their LLM-based apps, the package
    includes facilities for prompt engineering, tool usage, multi-turn dialog,
    and model graded evaluations.
